@baseUrl = http://localhost:8101

### 1) Cache MISS — first read (DB query expected)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### 2) Cache HIT — same product, no DB query
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### 3) Evict cache (simulates TTL expiry)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/cache/products/1

### 4) Cache MISS again after eviction
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/1

### 5) Another product — cold read
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/products/42
